database structure

table name: templates

id int
name varchar(20)
rating int
description varchar(400)
used_personal int
used_all int
author varchar(50)
author_email varchar(100)
send_mail bit
shared_date date
elements varchar(2000)
tags varchar(500)
picture image

example of a record: 32, Name of List, 3, bla bla, 4, 341, ion, ion@ion.com, 0, 20-02-1023;Shirt,Coat,Pants,Suit,Ball,Sun screen;sea side,summer


table name: lists

name varchar(20)
elements varchar(2500)
selected varchar(500)
picture image
thumbnail image

example of a record: Name of List;Shirt,Coat,Pants,Suit,Ball,Sun screen;0,0,0,1,0,1


local properties

last_sync date       ex: '02-10-2011'
not_synced string    ex: '3,6,12,43,2'